#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.80"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.80:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.80:0.2"
msgid "8. Ākaṅkhavagga"
msgstr "8. If You Want"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.80:0.3"
msgid "80. Āghātapaṭivinayasutta"
msgstr "80. Getting Rid of Resentment"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.151"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.80:1.1"
msgid "“Dasayime, bhikkhave, āghātapaṭivinayā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these ten methods to get rid of resentment."

msgctxt "an10.80:1.2"
msgid "Katame dasa?"
msgstr "What ten?"

msgctxt "an10.80:1.3"
msgid "‘Anatthaṃ me acari, taṃ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṃ paṭivineti, "
msgstr ""
"Thinking: ‘They did wrong by me, but what can I possibly do?’ you get rid of "
"resentment. "

msgctxt "an10.80:1.4"
msgid "‘anatthaṃ me carati, taṃ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṃ paṭivineti, "
msgstr "Thinking: ‘They are doing wrong by me …’ … "

msgctxt "an10.80:1.5"
msgid "‘anatthaṃ me carissati, taṃ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṃ paṭivineti, "
msgstr "‘They will do wrong by me …’ … "

msgctxt "an10.80:1.6"
msgid "piyassa me manāpassa anatthaṃ acari … pe …"
msgstr "‘They did wrong by someone I love …’ …"

msgctxt "an10.80:1.7"
msgid "carati … pe …"
msgstr "‘They are doing wrong by someone I love …’"

msgctxt "an10.80:1.8"
msgid ""
"carissati, taṃ kutettha labbhāti āghātaṃ paṭivineti, appiyassa me amanāpassa "
"atthaṃ acari … pe …"
msgstr ""
"‘They will do wrong by someone I love …’ … They helped someone I dislike …’ …"

msgctxt "an10.80:1.9"
msgid "atthaṃ carati … pe …"
msgstr "‘They are helping someone I dislike …’ …"

msgctxt "an10.80:1.10"
msgid "atthaṃ carissati, taṃ kutettha labbhāti āghātaṃ paṭivineti, "
msgstr ""
"Thinking: ‘They will help someone I dislike, but what can I possibly do?’ "
"you get rid of resentment. "

msgctxt "an10.80:1.11"
msgid "aṭṭhāne ca na kuppati—"
msgstr "And you don’t get angry for no reason."

msgctxt "an10.80:1.12"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, dasa āghātapaṭivinayā”ti."
msgstr "These are the ten ways of getting rid of resentment.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.80:1.13"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.80:1.14"
msgid "Ākaṅkhavaggo tatiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.80:2.1"
msgid "Ākaṅkho kaṇṭako iṭṭhā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.80:2.2"
msgid "vaḍḍhi ca migasālāya;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.80:2.3"
msgid "Tayo dhammā ca kāko ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.80:2.4"
msgid "nigaṇṭhā dve ca āghātāti."
msgstr ""
